ion","text":"n.分离，分裂（a sharp cleavage)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dxs'd3nk{n]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：dis（不）+junction（连接）→不再连接→分离"}]},{"number":151,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<< GRE 词汇精选 乱序版"},{"type":"text","text":"individuality and those that emphasize obedience to rules and cooperation with"},{"type":"text","text":"others reflects a conflict that arises from the values on which these objectives"},{"type":"text","text":"are based."},{"type":"entry","text":"virtuosity","headword":"virtuosity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 精湛技I5(great technical skill)"},{"type":"text","text":"[v3:rtfu'a:sati]"},{"type":"text","text":"Winsor McCay, the cartoonist, could draw with incredible virtuosity: his comic"},{"type":"text","text":"strip about Little Nemo was characterized by marvelous draftsmanship and"},{"type":"text","text":"sequencing."},{"type":"entry","text":"immolate","headword":"immolate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 牺牲，献条(to offer or kill as a sacrifice)"},{"type":"text","text":"['rmalert]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：im（在-之上）+mola（用作察品的肉）+te→放上蔡品→栖牲"},{"type":"entry","text":"justification","headword":"justification"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.正当的理由(an acceptable reason);辩护(the act of justifying)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,d3Astrfr'ker{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆来自justify（v证明是正当的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"jejune","headword":"jejune"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.空洞的(devoid of significance);不成熟的(not mature)"},{"type":"text","text":"[d3r'dzu:n]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：jejun（空的）+e→空洞的"},{"type":"entry","text":"versatile","headword":"versatile"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 多才多艺的(having many different kinds of skills); 多用途的(having many"},{"type":"text","text":"['v3:rsatl]"},{"type":"text","text":"different uses)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：vers（转）+atile→可向多个方向转的→多才多艺的"},{"type":"entry","text":"moribund","headword":"moribund"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.即将结束的（coming to an end);垂死的（dying)"},{"type":"text","text":"['mo:rrbAnd]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：mori死）+bund（看作bound，边界）→在死的边界徘徊→垂死的"},{"type":"text","text":"One of Detroit’'s great success stories tells of Lee lacocca's revitalization of"},{"type":"text","text":"the moribunc Chrysler Corporation, turning it into a vigorous competitor."},{"type":"entry","text":"voracious","headword":"voracious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.狼吞虎咽的，贪吃的（having a huge appetite)；贪婪的，贪得无厌的"},{"type":"text","text":"[va'rerfas]"},{"type":"text","text":"(excessively eager; insatiable)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：vor（吃）+acious（多…·的）→吃得多的→狼吞虎咽的：贪婪的"},{"type":"entry","text":"overthrow","headword":"overthrow"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 推副;终上(to throw over; overturn) n. 推翻;终i上(an instance of overthrowing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[auvar'Brau]"},{"type":"entry","text":"dejected","headword":"dejected"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj泪丧的，失望的，灰心的(in low spirits; depressed; disheartened)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dr'dzektid]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：de（向下）+ject（扔）+ed→被扔掉的→沮丧的，失望的，灰心的"},{"type":"entry","text":"abstemious","headword":"abstemious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 有节制的，节俭的(moderate in eating and drinking: temperate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ab'sti:mias]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：abs（脱离）+tem（酒）+ious→不喝酒→有节制的"},{"type":"text","text":"abstemiousness（n.节制;适中)"}]},{"number":152,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 12 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"orthodox","headword":"orthodox"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 正统的(conforming to the usual beliefs of established doctrines)"},{"type":"text","text":"[':rθada:ks]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ortho（正，直）+dox（观点）→正统观点的→正统的"},{"type":"text","text":"图 orthodoxy (n.正统观念)"},{"type":"entry","text":"equable","headword":"equable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj稳定的，不变的(not varying or fluctuating: steady);(脾气）温和的(tranquil,"},{"type":"text","text":"['ekwabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"serene)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：equ（平等）+able→能够平等的→稳定的"},{"type":"entry","text":"impregnable","he