ous→守护神的→神的"},{"type":"text","text":"['nu:minas]"},{"type":"entry","text":"interdisciplinary","headword":"interdisciplinary"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 跨学科的(covering more than one area of study)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,ntar'disaplrneri]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：inter（在中间）+disciplinary（学科的）→跨学科的"},{"type":"text","text":"图interdisciplinary course跨学科课程"},{"type":"text","text":"interdisciplinarity（n.跨学科性：多学科性）"},{"type":"entry","text":"adroit","headword":"adroit"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj熟练的，灵巧的（skilful, expert,dexterous)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'drort]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：a（加强）+droit（灵巧）→灵巧的"},{"type":"text","text":"adroitly（adv.熟练地;敏捷地）"},{"type":"entry","text":"inveterate","headword":"inveterate"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.积习已深的，根深蒂固的（habitual，chronic)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（使）+veter（老，旧）+ate→成为l旧东西的→积习已深的"},{"type":"text","text":"[In'vetarat]"}]},{"number":153,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"heresy","headword":"heresy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 异端邪说(a religious belief opposed to the orthodox doctrines)"},{"type":"text","text":"['herasi]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：here（这里）+sy（看作say，说）→非熟悉的本地人所说的→异端邪说"},{"type":"entry","text":"cunning","headword":"cunning"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj狡的，奸诈的(clever at deceiving people)：灵巧的，精巧的(ingenious)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kanin]"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.狡猾，奸诈(cunning behavior or quality)"},{"type":"entry","text":"aversion","headword":"aversion"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.厌恶，反感（an intense dislike; loathing)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'v3:r3n]"},{"type":"text","text":"aversion toward sb./sth. 对▪的厌恶"},{"type":"entry","text":"canonical","headword":"canonical"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 符合规定的(according to, or ordered by church canon);经典的"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka'na:nrkl]"},{"type":"text","text":"orthodox"},{"type":"entry","text":"extremist","headword":"extremist"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.极端主义者(a person who holds extreme views)"},{"ty