d":"strident"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.尖锐的，剩耳的(characterized by harsh sound)"},{"type":"text","text":"['straidnt]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：stri（看作stride，大步走）+dent（凹痕）→大步走进凹坑传来尖声大叫→"},{"type":"text","text":"尖锐的"},{"type":"entry","text":"sidestep","headword":"sidestep"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 横跨—步躲避(to take a step to the side to avoid);回避(to avoid)"},{"type":"text","text":"[saidstep]"},{"type":"text","text":"bypass, evade"},{"type":"entry","text":"humor","headword":"humor"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 纵容，迁就(to comply with the mood or whim; indulge)"},{"type":"text","text":"[hju:mar]"},{"type":"text","text":"图humor最常见的意思是“当默”→用留默的方式迁就小错"},{"type":"entry","text":"petrify","headword":"petrify"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. (使)石化(to convert into stone); (使)下呆(to confound with fear or awe)"},{"type":"text","text":"['petrfar]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：petr（石头）+ify→（使）石化"},{"type":"entry","text":"veto","headword":"veto"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.否决，禁上(an authoritative prohibition; interdiction)：否决权"},{"type":"text","text":"['vi:tau]"},{"type":"text","text":"圆在拉丁文中，veto的意思是“我不准”（1forbid），在英语里则表示“否决”或"},{"type":"text","text":"“否决权”。"},{"type":"entry","text":"adventitious","headword":"adventitious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 偶然的(accidental, casual)"},{"type":"text","text":"[aedven'tifas]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ad（向）+vent（到来，来临）+itious（有性质的）一→（突然）到来的→偶然的"},{"type":"entry","text":"invidious","headword":"invidious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.葱人反感的，导致伤害和仇恨的，招人嫉妒的（tending to cause discontent,"},{"type":"text","text":"[In'vidias]"},{"type":"text","text":"harm, animosity, or envy)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（不）+vid（看）+ious→不看的→惹人反感的"},{"type":"entry","text":"prolix","headword":"prolix"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj说话啰哮的，长的（unduly prolonged)"},{"type":"text","text":"['praulrks]"},{"type":"text","text":"wordy"},{"type":"text","text":"prolixity（n.长，啰咳）"},{"type":"entry","text":"frenzy","headword":"frenzy"},{"type":"d